      "line": 24,
      "message": "I dont think you need a specific script. Not sure what this 'find' do?\nSomething like this should work (archives dir is automatically saved for later trouble shooting - available in jenkins after the test)\n\ncd $WORKSPACE/archives\ngit clone \"https://gerrit.o-ran-sc.org/r/nonrtric\"\n\nCLONE_PATH=$WORKSPACE/archives/nonrtric/test/auto-test \nROBOT_VARIABLES=\"-b debug.log -v CLONE_PATH:${CLONE_PATH}\"",
      "author": {
